# Seguenzia wareni

Seguenzia wareni is a species of extremely small deep water sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Seguenziidae.
Description
The length of the shell attains 2.8 mm.
Distribution
This marine species occurs in the South Pacific Ocean off New Caledonia.
